---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — elect-rix.tech" description="The vision behind the Workstation Duo and elect-rix.tech">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-8">About</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        <strong class="text-text">elect-rix.tech</strong> is an experiment in controlled independence — a website
        built on local hardware, served by global infrastructure, and authored by an expanding vision.
      </p>

      <p>
        The <strong class="text-text">Workstation Duo</strong> powers everything behind this domain:
      </p>

      <ul class="space-y-3 pl-5 list-disc marker:text-accent">
        <li>
          <span class="text-text font-medium">butters</span> — Intel i9-14900K, NVIDIA RTX 5070 Ti 16GB,
          32GB RAM. Handles content drafting, website builds, and Ollama inference.
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="text-text font-medium">proff</span> — Intel i7, dual AMD RX 9060 XT.
          Handles batch image generation via ComfyUI, parallel processing, and media pipelines.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Nothing here is outsourced that doesn't need to be. The AI stack is local. The site is static.
        The only cloud dependency is the edge network itself — Cloudflare Pages — because no basement server
        can beat 300+ global PoPs.
      </p>

      <p>
        The vision is still forming. This site exists to make sure the platform is ready when the direction
        reveals itself.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 p-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">Technology Stack</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {
          [
            'Astro', 'Tailwind CSS', 'bun', 'Cloudflare Pages',
            'Ollama', 'ComfyUI', 'Cloudflare', 'PostgreSQL'
          ].map((tech) => (
            <span class="px-3 py-1 text-sm rounded-full bg-accent/10 text-accent-bright border border-accent/20">
              {tech}
            </span>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>